{"tid":844511,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"做4小時健身應硬則硬 孫耀威：老婆見我有乳溝心跳加速","createTime":"2018-10-02T02:52:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-02T18:50:03.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"467fdb70a703b09779770633f59a9d79885b3083","tid":844511,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T02:52:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/bySENNP57jsaCGSFXKbhzw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20181001f220422.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FbySENNP57jsaCGSFXKbhzw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20181001f220422.jpg&h=42c0e6dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【星島日報報道】孫耀威（Eric）首次於香港演出國慶騷，他表示09年曾代表香港到世博以普通話擔任發佈會主持，當時好驚，因為他自覺好多懶音，所以覺得以後參與做騷都是表演較好。忙於為演唱會操肌的他，直言昨日做足4小時健身運動，現時也感覺腳仔軟，更笑謂應硬則硬，脾氣夠硬。他說：「依然瘦了接近6kg，開始可以增加肌肉，現在積極健身同練琴。」<br />\n<br />\n問太太陳美詩可滿意他身形？Eric說：「有次我趴響度睇書，佢話我有乳溝，有少少心跳加速的感覺。（多手摸你？）結婚有一段時間，有少少衝擊係好事。我都會Keep住身形，希望不會反彈，我身上的西裝原本著好fit，依家變成大碼，好彩依家興鬆身。」（攝影：張家宜）"},{"pid":"a9f3bfa6d370fd47343a3740b17937b0aa34d5cf","tid":844511,"uid":56401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"467fdb70a703b09779770633f59a9d79885b3083","tid":844511,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T02:52:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/bySENNP57jsaCGSFXKbhzw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20181001f220422.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FbySENNP57jsaCGSFXKbhzw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20181001f220422.jpg&h=42c0e6dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【星島日報報道】孫耀威（Eric）首次於香港演出國慶騷，他表示09年曾代表香港到世博以普通話擔任發佈會